Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Gets the current angular velocity of this entity. The angular velocity
of a physics object is a vector that passes through the center of mass.
The direction of this vector defines the axis of rotation and the
magnitude defines the rate of rotation about the axis in radians per
second.

Usage
-----

*vector* getAngularVelocity()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

